column5: What are you contacting us about?

column6:
Hello, 

I recently discovered the IDEA Venture accelerator for Northeastern-affiliated entrepreneur and am interested and excited about pursuing this endeavor. 

I graduated with my M.S. Sustainable Building Systems from NEU's College of Engineering in 2015. I am now out in the working world but have a few ideas that need a bit of support. 

I would appreciate any help you can offer in navigating this program. Thank you!

Sincerely,
Ivy
